{"title":"Java中floorMod方法的理解","date":"2020-02-28T06:11:01.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年2月28日","L":"2020/02/28","MM-DD":"02-28"},"author":"Clever Anastasia","thumbnail":"https://s2.ax1x.com/2020/02/28/3BTFwq.png","link":"2020/02/28/zaliang03","comments":true,"tags":["Java","To be professional"],"categories":["杂粮库"],"updated":"2020-02-28T07:28:53.902Z","content":"<h2 id=\"概念对比\">概念对比<a href=\"#概念对比\" title=\"概念对比\"></a></h2><div class=\"φcz\"><div class=\"φdb\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th>名称</th><th>含义</th><th>示例</th></tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td>%</td><td>求余(rem)</td><td>(+4 % -3)== +1</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>floorMod()</td><td>取模(mod)</td><td>floorMod(+4,-3)== -2</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div><h2 id=\"核心区别\">核心区别<a href=\"#核心区别\" title=\"核心区别\"></a></h2><p>对于整型数a，b来说，取模运算或者求余运算的方法都是：<br>1.求 整数商： c = a/b;<br>2.计算模或者余数： r = a - c*b.</p>\n<p>求模运算和求余运算在第一步不同: <strong>取余运算在取c的值时，向0方向舍入；而取模运算在计算c的值时，向负无穷方向舍入</strong>。</p>\n<p>例：</p>\n<div class=\"φcz\"><div class=\"φdb\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th style=\"padding:0\"></th><th>+4 % -3</th><th>floorMod(+4,-3)</th></tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td>a=</td><td>+4</td><td>+4</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>b=</td><td>-3</td><td>-3</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>c=</td><td><strong>-1</strong></td><td><strong>-2</strong></td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>r=</td><td>+1</td><td>-2</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div><h2 id=\"记忆点\">记忆点<a href=\"#记忆点\" title=\"记忆点\"></a></h2><p>当a,b同号时，求余运算与取模运算结果相同，符号与a（被除数）相同；否则，取模运算的符号与b（除数）相同。</p>\n","next":{"title":"换行与回车的区别","link":"2020/02/27/zaliang02"},"plink":"https://venanastasia.github.io/2020/02/28/zaliang03/","toc":[{"id":"概念对比","title":"概念对比","index":"1"},{"id":"核心区别","title":"核心区别","index":"2"},{"id":"记忆点","title":"记忆点","index":"3"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Clever Anastasia","license":"No permission to reproduce. Anastasia only.😎"}}